Output demo/gifs/hero.gif
Set Height 820
Source demo/tapes/_setup.tape

# Render the startup header, then reveal a clean screen (the `clear; …` line is
# wiped before the header prints, so only the header + prompt are shown).
Type "clear; echo_header" Enter
Show
Sleep 1.2s

Type "up" Sleep 400ms Enter
Sleep 3.5s
